bearer-of-at(I, G, T) :- inheres-in(S, I), instantiates(S, G), occupies-temporal-region(S, T).
is-a_(D, D) :- instance-of(D, C), instance-of(C, C).
is-a_(C, E) :- is-a_(C, D), is-a(D, E).
continuant-part-of-at(I, S, T) :- in-sequence-number(I, S, N), occupies-temporal-region(I, T).
instance-of_(E, D) :- instance-of(E, C), is-a(C, D).
continuant-part-of-at(A, B, T) :- member-part-of-at(A, B, T).
inheres-in(S1, I) :- subservice-at(S1, S2, T), inheres-in(S2, I).
class-of(E, N) :- instance-of(E, C), name(C, N).
